snippet.title: Ribbiting Saga Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Please visit our Kickstarter to help bring Ribbiting Saga to life!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/happyogre/ribbiting-saga

Also check out our discord if you want to chat with us! We never want to stop talking about games : https://www.discord.gg/K8ZWABB

This is the Kickstarter Trailer for Ribbiting Saga  : A snappy SNES-inspired action adventure game with dungeons and bosses that change based on your choices. Laugh and get your butt kicked as you hop your way through puzzle-filled dungeons! Find hidden items and help quirky characters to get stronger.
